  [2]: https://stackoverflow.com/a/34784290/1504556
  [3]: https://github.com/javaee/metro-jax-ws/blob/master/jaxws-ri/samples/src/main/samples/efficient_handler/
  [4]: https://github.com/javaee/metro-jax-ws/

